WEBVTT

00:01:57.586 --> 00:02:01.156
srž dobrog poduzetništva.

00:02:01.156 --> 00:02:03.674
Pa što to vidim u našoj budućnosti danas,

00:02:03.674 --> 00:02:05.676
pitate me?

00:02:05.676 --> 00:02:07.331
Vidim vile,

00:02:07.331 --> 00:02:12.121
kao u gnjevnoj gomili s vilama,

00:02:12.121 --> 00:02:17.335
jer dok ljudi poput nas plutokrata

00:02:17.335 --> 00:02:20.866
žive onkraj snova o pohlepi,

00:02:20.866 --> 00:02:23.779
ostalih 99 posto naših kolega građana

00:02:23.779 --> 00:02:26.592
ostaje sve dalje i dalje za nama.

00:02:26.592 --> 00:02:29.080
1980, gornjih 1% Amerikanaca

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:31.558
je dijelio oko 8% nacionalnog [dohotka],